## Métodos {.highlight-last style="font-size: 55%; text-align: center;"}

$$\small
alfdigital_{ij} = \gamma_{10} \text{sexo.cmc}_i + \gamma_{20} \text{iiseb.cmc}_i 
+ \gamma_{30} \text{expcompu.cmc}_i + \gamma_{40} \text{autoeffgen.cmc}_i + \gamma_{50} \text{aprendizaje_escuela.cmc}_i + \gamma_{01} \text{adm_digital}_j + \gamma_{02} \text{logpib}_j + \mu_{0j}$$

